long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
CartInsight delivers 1-click intelligence for online stores covering all aspects from cart platform used, location, contact information, technographic profile, category of business and a lot more. 

CartInsight uses state-of-the-art data discovery and mining technology to uncover actionable intelligence that can be leveraged by sales, marketing, ecommerce, market research and other teams. 

CartInsight chrome extension is free to use and you can upgrade to a paid version at any time to get full access to all online stores and their detailed sales intelligence data in one place. More details here: https://www.cartinsight.io
